It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves the use of neural networks for learning and classification. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves the use of AI techniques for translation evaluation. The paper also mentions the use of sentence embeddings, which could place it under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper mentions the use of syntactic and semantic information, which could place it under cs.CV (Computer Vision) as these are important concepts in natural language processing and computer vision.
